metadata.name: Tokyo Future Girl
metadata.description:
The event will be held in Tokyo in October 2022. The creators who will exhibit their works at this event have original characters, and I have borrowed their characters.
They will be the ones who will shine in the world in the future. I dream of a future where these women exist in the same world line, live in the same world, and shine together.
This world was created by my good friend "VEL.

Through this work, I was able to realize through the characters that I am in the same place with people who are working in the same place like this.

Thank you, dear creators.
onigiriman tsurushima sashimi tama5  KAI VEL
